cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper deals with the verification of safety properties of closed-loop systems using neural networks as controllers. This falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also extensively uses machine learning techniques, specifically neural networks, which makes it relevant to the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of reachability tools, which is a common technique in the field of numerical analysis and scientific computing, making it relevant to the category of neural networks (cs.NE).
